    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Shutters having louvers or slats positioned vertically in a frame rather than horizontally; distinct from "vertical blinds," which have vertical slats or panels, but are typically lighter-weight and attached at the top rather than in a frame.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
